metadata.name: Crystal Babies
metadata.description:
Somewhere in a long lost land
Far from trees and golden sand
Reigns a Kingdom made of snow
Where crystal beings and plants grow

And in the mind of each ice being
Hides a story with its own meaning
Each story paves the vision of the future
A destiny that can't be punctured
As what lies in the minds of the many
Manifests as the next generation's journey
